            <ul>
                <li>Speech-language pathologist graduated from Université de Montréal in 2015 </li>
                <li>Doctorate in Speech-language pathology sciences from Université de Montréal in 2023</li>
                <li>Postdoctoral research fellow at Johns Hopkins Hospital in Baltimore, USA </li>
